{"tid":874262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民稱期待近30年終可登上港珠澳大橋 支那客：四季變化一目了然","createTime":"2018-10-24T05:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T06:18:19.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"acf2750ec8b3215a72858bbc301ba4cd515a313f","tid":874262,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:23:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540351602_6af0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540351602_6af0.jpg&h=bdac3d82&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n歷時9年興建的港珠澳大橋首日通車，不少旅行社把握商機，舉辦「首發團」，標榜即日來回香港至澳門或珠海。張生張太參加了珠海一日遊「首發團」，兩人均表示特地趁大橋首日通車參加，認為香港口岸大樓十分美麗，橋上景色優美。居於天水圍曾女士在今晨5時已起床準備，她稱自己有不少朋友在珠海一帶，預料日後也會多利用港珠澳大橋往返支那。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540346594_7dd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540346594_7dd0.jpg&h=d16c7852&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n有支那遊客來港並專誠在通車首日體驗橫跨大橋。有廣州遊客表示從珠海來港只需45分鐘，而家沿岸景色優美：「有天空啦、有船啦，一年四季景色一目了然！」上海遊客陳先生表示，特意選擇今天經港珠澳大橋到澳門，他早前已在支那預約購票，並在香港口岸透過自助取票機取票。陳表示，取票機操作方便，整個過程不到10秒。市民方先生更興奮得向記者高舉其剛買的澳門車票，他稱自己已期待港珠澳大橋近30年，早已急不及待乘巴士登上大橋。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540346594_f859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540346594_f859.jpg&h=b112526e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181024/58828838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58828838&d=PLqY17On9GjrtTpqPr5A8TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e93b6c50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58828838&h=f8cc0e81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181024/58828838</a>"},{"pid":"05ae5cac52eb812eebf190672072f2f3948554f2","tid":874262,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，合和實業主席胡應湘在80年代已提議建連接香港和珠海大橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。胡昨獲邀出席大橋通車儀式時，讚賞大橋水準很好，「無論從設計或者施工都做得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，形容自己圓了心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「呢個唔係我嘅心願，係大灣區居民嘅心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。"},{"pid":"b7de1ac562fc85739297da38fbb5916587d67826","tid":874262,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540353521_8414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540353521_8414.jpg&h=e8e79eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州旅客由珠海來港，認為大橋景色優美風景怡人，更指四季變化一目了然。</div>"},{"pid":"3aa66ee2228c25dee69ce5320b58ab3d77a6a706","tid":874262,"uid":2772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b7de1ac562fc85739297da38fbb5916587d67826","tid":874262,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540353521_8414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2